        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "Labor Department of Chhattisgarh State started this scheme &amp;amp;quot;Nirmaan Shramik  Ke Bachchon Hetu  Utkrasht Khel Protsaahan Yojana&amp;amp;quot; for Construction Workers on 23 May 2017. The main objective of the scheme to provide financial to encourage the studdents for sports.\n&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;\n\n&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "Incentive amount will be provided to the children who perform excellently at the district / division / state / national level in all recognized sports as follows -\n\n1. Amount at district level: ₹ 1,000/-\n1. Amount at divisional level: ₹ 2,000/-\n1. Amount at state level: ₹ 5,000/-\n1. Amount at National level : ₹ 50,000/-\n\n",
